n<br />\n　　消防處職工總會主席聶元風以個人身份參加遊行，指出紀律部隊大部份人對判刑感到不開心，「唔知條尺點度」，各紀律部隊將開會討論如何向警隊協會提供支援。</blockquote><br />\n紀律部隊無紀律 仲學人講要減刑<br />\n無撚野呀"},{"pid":"9f97e02dce2aa3979e4a53d80411517a7de43ab9","tid":126243,"uid":20903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:02:45.000Z","msg":"要求釋放所有做左爸爸既囚犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca03f245cc27a300583f026b8817960afd6ed2a","tid":126243,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"為左奶共賺錢搞深圳醫院，寧願做臭自己個名，正仆街"},{"pid":"6f4af7a96c9259e38004674ccc379fce33537483","tid":126243,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"送埋個仔入去咪有返爸爸囉"},{"pid":"98f11007ec58fb2e8068a3ac59adb591442c6794","tid":126243,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要求釋放所有做左爸爸既囚犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔只爸爸<br />\n係全部犯人都要釋放<br />\n做左爸爸既會令人地無左爸爸<br />\n做左媽媽既會令人地無左媽媽<br />\n未做爸爸媽媽既會令人地爸爸媽媽無左個仔女<br />\n真係聞者傷心 聽者流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277b0ac728790e3c8d3a89568828a9e58c27673b","tid":126243,"uid":5603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:07:26.000Z","msg":"快d去生仔 做左爸爸唔使坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ca1c65b84f1db4039b3be20fe25af53c451689","tid":126243,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:08:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"